<div class="wrap"><section class="daysec" id="day0">
  <div class="dayhead"><div class="eyebrow">Dec 9 · Wed</div><h2>Arrival → Lake Shikotsu</h2><div class="cn">新千歳空港 → 支笏湖 → 苫小牧</div><div class="chips"><span class="chip">✈️ Land 11:55</span><span class="chip">🚗 Car 13:00 · ETC card</span><span class="chip">⏱ ~1h driving</span></div></div>
  <div class="hotel"><div class="ic">🏨</div><div><b>New Tomakomai Prince Hotel Nagomi</b> <span style="color:#A9BFDC">· 新苫小牧プリンスホテル和</span><div class="sub">No meals · dinner in town · <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=New%20Tomakomai%20Prince%20Hotel%20Nagomi" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Open in Maps ↗</a></div></div></div>
  <div class="tl"><div class="stop"><div class="time">13:00</div><div class="card"><h3>Pick up rental car </h3><div class="names">新千歳空港 レンタカー</div><div class="note">Confirm studless tyres fitted + take the ETC card. Load luggage smart — it's 15 days.</div><div class="links"><a class="map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=New%20Chitose%20Airport%20rental%20car" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📍 Maps</a></div></div></div><div class="stop"><div class="time">14:20</div><div class="card"><h3>Lake Shikotsu <span class="badge hot">📕 小红书HOT</span></h3><div class="names">支笏湖 · Shikotsu-ko</div><div class="note">Japan's clearest lake — never freezes despite the snow. The 'Shikotsu blue' against white is your opening reel.</div><div class="links"><a class="map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Lake%20Shikotsu" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📍 Maps</a><a class="xhs" href="https://www.xiaohongshu.com/search_result?keyword=%E6%94%AF%E7%AC%8F%E6%B9%96%20%E5%86%AC" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📕 小红书</a><a class="ig" href="https://www.instagram.com/explore/tags/lakeshikotsu/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📸 IG</a><a class="yt" href="https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=Lake%20Shikotsu%20winter" target="_blank" rel="noopener">▶ YouTube</a></div></div></div><div class="stop"><div class="time">14:50</div><div class="card"><h3>Yamasen Iron Bridge <span class="badge hot">📕 小红书HOT</span></h3><div class="names">山線鉄橋</div><div class="note">Red英式 iron bridge over the Chitose river mouth — the classic 打卡 frame with the lake behind.</div><div class="links"><a class="map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Yamasen%20Bridge%20Lake%20Shikotsu" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📍 Maps</a><a class="xhs" href="https://www.xiaohongshu.com/search_result?keyword=%E5%B1%B1%E7%B7%9A%E9%89%84%E6%A9%8B" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📕 小红书</a></div></div></div><div class="stop"><div class="time">15:35</div><div class="card"><h3>Shichijo Waterfall (optional) </h3><div class="names">七条大滝</div><div class="note">Only if on schedule — dusk-marginal. Skip without guilt if the flight ran late.</div><div class="links"><a class="map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Shichijo%20Otaki%20Tomakomai" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📍 Maps</a></div></div></div><div class="stop"><div class="time">18:00</div><div class="card"><h3>Hokki clam dinner <span class="badge eat">🍜 EAT</span></h3><div class="names">北寄貝(ホッキ)料理</div><div class="note">Tomakomai is Japan's No.1 hokki landing port. Hokki curry or hokki sushi near the hotel — the only right first dinner here.</div><div class="links"><a class="map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Marutoma%20Shokudo%20Tomakomai" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📍 Maps</a><a class="xhs" href="https://www.xiaohongshu.com/search_result?keyword=%E8%8B%AB%E5%B0%8F%E7%89%A7%20%E5%8C%97%E5%AF%84%E8%B4%9D" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📕 小红书</a><a class="yt" href="https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=Tomakomai%20hokki%20curry" target="_blank" rel="noopener">▶ YouTube</a></div></div></div></div><div class="tipbox"><b>Trip-wide reminders:</b> International Driving Permit + Singapore licence · winter driving = double Google's time estimates on rural roads · petrol before rural legs · コンビニ onigiri is a legitimate lunch backup.</div></section><section class="daysec" id="day1">
  <div class="dayhead"><div class="eyebrow">Dec 10 · Thu</div><h2>Noboribetsu Hell Valley</h2><div class="cn">登別 → 室蘭</div><div class="chips"><span class="chip">🚗 50 min + 30 min</span><span class="chip">♨️ Onsen town day</span></div></div>
  <div class="hotel"><div class="ic">🏨</div><div><b>Dormy Inn Higashi-Muroran</b> <span style="color:#A9BFDC">· ドーミーイン東室蘭</span><div class="sub">2 rooms · onsen · FREE 21:30 yonaki ramen — don't skip · <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Dormy%20Inn%20Higashi%20Muroran" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Open in Maps ↗</a></div></div></div>
  <div class="tl"><div class="stop"><div class="time">10:00</div><div class="card"><h3>Jigokudani (Hell Valley) <span class="badge hot">📕 小红书HOT</span></h3><div class="names">地獄谷</div><div class="note">Steam is thickest against cold morning air — arrive by 10 for the drama shots on the boardwalk.</div><div class="links"><a class="map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Jigokudani%20Noboribetsu" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📍 Maps</a><a class="xhs" href="https://www.xiaohongshu.com/search_result?keyword=%E7%99%BB%E5%88%AB%E5%9C%B0%E7%8B%B1%E8%B0%B7" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📕 小红书</a><a class="ig" href="https://www.instagram.com/explore/tags/noboribetsu/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📸 IG</a><a class="yt" href="https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=Noboribetsu%20Jigokudani%20winter" target="_blank" rel="noopener">▶ YouTube</a></div></div></div><div class="stop onsen"><div class="time">10:45</div><div class="card"><h3>Oyunuma + natural river footbath <span class="badge hot">📕 小红书HOT</span> <span class="badge onsenb">♨️ ONSEN</span></h3><div class="names">大湯沼 · 大湯沼川天然足湯</div><div class="note">Feet in a hot river inside a snowy forest, free. Bring a small towel. The day's best video content.</div><div class="links"><a class="map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Oyunumagawa%20natural%20footbath" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📍 Maps</a><a class="xhs" href="https://www.xiaohongshu.com/search_result?keyword=%E5%A4%A7%E6%B1%A4%E6%B2%BC%E5%B7%9D%20%E5%A4%A9%E7%84%B6%E8%B6%B3%E6%B1%A4" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📕 小红书</a><a class="yt" href="https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=Oyunuma%20footbath%20winter" target="_blank" rel="noopener">▶ YouTube</a></div></div></div><div class="stop"><div class="time">12:30</div><div class="card"><h3>Lunch on Gokuraku-dori <span class="badge eat">🍜 EAT</span></h3><div class="names">極楽通り温泉街</div><div class="note">Onsen Ichiba for kama-meshi / seafood. Demon statues line the street — the boys will find them.</div><div class="links"><a class="map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Onsen%20Ichiba%20Noboribetsu" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📍 Maps</a></div></div></div><div class="stop"><div class="time">14:00</div><div class="card"><h3>Sengen Park geyser </h3><div class="names">泉源公園</div><div class="note">Geyser vents every ~3 hours; even idle, the demon clubs make a quick fun stop.</div><div class="links"><a class="map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Sengen%20Park%20Noboribetsu" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📍 Maps</a></div></div></div><div class="stop"><div class="time">15:15</div><div class="card"><h3>Cape Chikyu sunset <span class="badge hot">📕 小红书HOT</span></h3><div class="names">地球岬 · Cape Chikyu</div><div class="note">Clifftop lighthouse over the Pacific — time it for the 16:00 sunset. 'Earth Cape' lives up to the name.</div><div class="links"><a class="map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Cape%20Chikyu%20Muroran" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📍 Maps</a><a class="xhs" href="https://www.xiaohongshu.com/search_result?keyword=%E5%9C%B0%E7%90%83%E5%B2%AC" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📕 小红书</a><a class="yt" href="https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=Cape%20Chikyu%20Muroran" target="_blank" rel="noopener">▶ YouTube</a></div></div></div><div class="stop"><div class="time">18:30</div><div class="card"><h3>Muroran yakitori <span class="badge eat">🍜 EAT</span></h3><div class="names">室蘭やきとり</div><div class="note">The local quirk: it's PORK with mustard, not chicken. Then back for the free hotel ramen at 21:30.</div><div class="links"><a class="map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Muroran%20yakitori%20Higashi%20Muroran" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📍 Maps</a><a class="xhs" href="https://www.xiaohongshu.com/search_result?keyword=%E5%AE%A4%E5%85%B0%E7%83%A4%E4%B8%B2" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📕 小红书</a></div></div></div></div></section><section class="daysec" id="day2">
  <div class="dayhead"><div class="eyebrow">Dec 11 · Fri</div><h2>Lake Toya Onsen Night</h2><div class="cn">洞爺湖温泉</div><div class="chips"><span class="chip">🚗 40 min</span><span class="chip">♨️ Ryokan night · kaiseki</span><span class="chip">🎆 No fireworks in Dec — confirmed</span></div></div>
  <div class="hotel"><div class="ic">🏨</div><div><b>Toyako Manseikaku Lakeside Terrace</b> <span style="color:#A9BFDC">· 洞爺湖万世閣</span><div class="sub">Dinner + breakfast included · lakeview onsen · <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Toyako%20Manseikaku%20Hotel%20Lakeside%20Terrace" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Open in Maps ↗</a></div></div></div>
  <div class="tl"><div class="stop"><div class="time">09:45</div><div class="card"><h3>Showa Shinzan + Usuzan Ropeway <span class="badge hot">📕 小红书HOT</span></h3><div class="names">昭和新山 · 有珠山ロープウェイ</div><div class="note">A volcano born in 1943 in a farmer's field. Summit deck = crater + lake + sea in one frame.</div><div class="links"><a class="map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Usuzan%20Ropeway" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📍 Maps</a><a class="xhs" href="https://www.xiaohongshu.com/search_result?keyword=%E6%98%AD%E5%92%8C%E6%96%B0%E5%B1%B1%20%E6%9C%89%E7%8F%A0%E5%B1%B1" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📕 小红书</a><a class="ig" href="https://www.instagram.com/explore/tags/laketoya/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📸 IG</a><a class="yt" href="https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=Mt%20Usu%20ropeway%20winter" target="_blank" rel="noopener">▶ YouTube</a></div></div></div><div class="stop"><div class="time">12:00</div><div class="card"><h3>Boyotei <span class="badge eat">🍜 EAT</span></h3><div class="names">望羊蹄</div><div class="note">1946 Western-style house; order the pork sauté. Quietly famous with locals, not a tour-bus stop.</div><div class="links"><a class="map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Boyotei%20Toyako" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📍 Maps</a><a class="xhs" href="https://www.xiaohongshu.com/search_result?keyword=%E6%B4%9E%E7%88%B7%E6%B9%96%20%E6%9C%9B%E7%BE%8A%E8%B9%84" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📕 小红书</a></div></div></div><div class="stop"><div class="time">13:30</div><div class="card"><h3>Lakeside sculpture stroll </h3><div class="names">洞爺湖畔 彫刻公園</div><div class="note">58 sculptures along the shore; winter boat to Nakajima island if sailings run.</div><div class="links"><a class="map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Lake%20Toya%20sculpture%20park" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📍 Maps</a></div></div></div><div class="stop onsen"><div class="time">15:00</div><div class="card"><h3>Check in → onsen BEFORE dinner <span class="badge onsenb">♨️ ONSEN</span></h3><div class="names">温泉 → 会席料理</div><div class="note">Bathe while daylight is still on the lake, kaiseki at 18:00, then the lakeview bath again after dark.</div><div class="links"><a class="map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Toyako%20Manseikaku" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📍 Maps</a></div></div></div></div></section><section class="daysec" id="day3">
  <div class="dayhead"><div class="eyebrow">Dec 12 · Sat</div><h2>Scenic Drive to Niseko</h2><div class="cn">洞爺湖 → 二世古</div><div class="chips"><span class="chip">🚗 Route 230 → 66</span><span class="chip">🗻 Yotei shows best before noon</span><span class="chip warn">📌 BOOK 2 dinners tonight</span></div></div>
  <div class="hotel"><div class="ic">🏨</div><div><b>Ki Niseko</b> <span style="color:#A9BFDC">· 綺ニセコ</span><div class="sub">2 nights · breakfast · onsen · at the gondola base · <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Ki%20Niseko%20Hotel" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Open in Maps ↗</a></div></div></div>
  <div class="tl"><div class="stop"><div class="time">09:45</div><div class="card"><h3>Lake Hill Farm gelato <span class="badge hot">📕 小红书HOT</span> <span class="badge eat">🍜 EAT</span></h3><div class="names">レークヒルファーム</div><div class="note">Gelato at −5°C with a Mt Yotei view — that IS the bit. XHS loves it.</div><div class="links"><a class="map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Lake%20Hill%20Farm%20Toyako" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📍 Maps</a><a class="xhs" href="https://www.xiaohongshu.com/search_result?keyword=Lake%20Hill%20Farm%20%E6%B4%9E%E7%88%B7%E6%B9%96" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📕 小红书</a><a class="yt" href="https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=Lake%20Hill%20Farm%20Hokkaido" target="_blank" rel="noopener">▶ YouTube</a></div></div></div><div class="stop"><div class="time">11:00</div><div class="card"><h3>Route 66 Yotei viewpoints <span class="badge hot">📕 小红书HOT</span></h3><div class="names">羊蹄山 · '蝦夷富士'</div><div class="note">'Ezo Fuji' hides by afternoon more often than morning — pull over the moment it's clear.</div><div class="links"><a class="map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Mount%20Yotei%20viewpoint%20Niseko" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📍 Maps</a><a class="xhs" href="https://www.xiaohongshu.com/search_result?keyword=%E7%BE%8A%E8%B9%84%E5%B1%B1" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📕 小红书</a><a class="ig" href="https://www.instagram.com/explore/tags/mtyotei/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📸 IG</a></div></div></div><div class="stop"><div class="time">12:00</div><div class="card"><h3>Lunch in Kutchan <span class="badge eat">🍜 EAT</span></h3><div class="names">倶知安</div><div class="note">Soup curry or a local izakaya — cheaper and more local than Hirafu village.</div><div class="links"><a class="map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Kutchan%20restaurants" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📍 Maps</a></div></div></div><div class="stop"><div class="time">14:00</div><div class="card"><h3>Niseko Takahashi Milk Kobo <span class="badge hot">📕 小红书HOT</span> <span class="badge eat">🍜 EAT</span></h3><div class="names">高橋牧場ミルク工房</div><div class="note">Cream puffs + drinking yoghurt with Yotei as the backdrop. Non-negotiable stop.</div><div class="links"><a class="map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Niseko%20Takahashi%20Dairy%20Farm%20Milk%20Kobo" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📍 Maps</a><a class="xhs" href="https://www.xiaohongshu.com/search_result?keyword=%E4%BA%8C%E4%B8%96%E8%B0%B7%20%E7%89%9B%E5%A5%B6%E5%B7%A5%E6%88%BF" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📕 小红书</a><a class="yt" href="https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=Milk%20Kobo%20Niseko" target="_blank" rel="noopener">▶ YouTube</a></div></div></div><div class="stop night"><div class="time">17:00</div><div class="card"><h3>Hirafu village night walk <span class="badge nightb">🌙 NIGHT</span> <span class="badge eat">🍜 EAT</span></h3><div class="names">ヒラフ坂</div><div class="note">Reserve BOTH nights' dinners now — December Hirafu fully books. Bang Bang (izakaya) / Niseko Loft Club (jingisukan) / An Dining.</div><div class="links"><a class="map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Hirafu%20village%20Niseko" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📍 Maps</a><a class="xhs" href="https://www.xiaohongshu.com/search_result?keyword=%E4%BA%8C%E4%B8%96%E8%B0%B7%20%E7%BE%8E%E9%A3%9F" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📕 小红书</a></div></div></div></div></section><section class="daysec" id="day4">
  <div class="dayhead"><div class="eyebrow">Dec 13 · Sun</div><h2>Ski Day · Split Crew</h2><div class="cn">グラン・ヒラフ滑雪日</div><div class="chips"><span class="chip">⛷ You + 14yo ski</span><span class="chip">☕ Wife + 19yo on foot</span><span class="chip">🚡 Non-skiers can ride gondola</span></div></div>
  <div class="hotel"><div class="ic">🏨</div><div><b>Ki Niseko</b> <span style="color:#A9BFDC">· 綺ニセコ</span><div class="sub">Onsen at 16:00 · dinner reservation from yesterday · <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Ki%20Niseko%20Hotel" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Open in Maps ↗</a></div></div></div>
  <div class="tl"><div class="stop"><div class="time">08:30</div><div class="card"><h3>Rentals + Grand Hirafu lift pass </h3><div class="names">グラン・ヒラフ</div><div class="note">Ki ski valet or Rhythm (2 min walk). Family Run & Ace greens suit 3-trip beginners; visibility best before noon.</div><div class="links"><a class="map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Grand%20Hirafu%20ski%20resort" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📍 Maps</a><a class="yt" href="https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=Grand%20Hirafu%20beginner%20run" target="_blank" rel="noopener">▶ YouTube</a></div></div></div><div class="stop"><div class="time">10:00</div><div class="card"><h3>Non-skiers: Gondola sightseeing ride <span class="badge hot">📕 小红书HOT</span></h3><div class="names">観光ゴンドラ</div><div class="note">Single-ride tickets for foot passengers — Yotei panorama, and they can watch you two come down.</div><div class="links"><a class="map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Hirafu%20Gondola" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📍 Maps</a><a class="xhs" href="https://www.xiaohongshu.com/search_result?keyword=%E4%BA%8C%E4%B8%96%E8%B0%B7%20%E7%BC%86%E8%BD%A6" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📕 小红书</a></div></div></div><div class="stop"><div class="time">11:00</div><div class="card"><h3>Non-skiers: café crawl + Graubünden <span class="badge eat">🍜 EAT</span></h3><div class="names">グラウビュンデン</div><div class="note">Green Farm Café → Hirafu-zaka bakeries → Graubünden's cult cookies (10 min walk). Browse Rhythm's gear floor.</div><div class="links"><a class="map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Graubunden%20Hirafu" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📍 Maps</a><a class="xhs" href="https://www.xiaohongshu.com/search_result?keyword=Graub%C3%BCnden%20%E4%BA%8C%E4%B8%96%E8%B0%B7" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📕 小红书</a></div></div></div><div class="stop"><div class="time">12:15</div><div class="card"><h3>Regroup: lunch at the base <span class="badge eat">🍜 EAT</span></h3><div class="names">山麓で合流</div><div class="note">Afternoon runs 13:00–15:00, gear back by 15:30.</div><div class="links"><a class="map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Grand%20Hirafu%20base" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📍 Maps</a></div></div></div><div class="stop onsen"><div class="time">16:00</div><div class="card"><h3>Ki onsen → village dinner <span class="badge onsenb">♨️ ONSEN</span> <span class="badge eat">🍜 EAT</span></h3><div class="names">温泉 → 夕食</div><div class="note">Legs in the rotenburo, then the reservation you made yesterday.</div><div class="links"><a class="map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Ki%20Niseko" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📍 Maps</a></div></div></div></div></section><section class="daysec" id="day5">
  <div class="dayhead"><div class="eyebrow">Dec 14 · Mon</div><h2>Yoichi Whisky → Otaru Canal</h2><div class="cn">余市 → 小樽運河</div><div class="chips"><span class="chip">🚗 Route 5 · ~1h45 total</span><span class="chip">📸 Canal blue hour 15:50–16:20</span></div></div>
  <div class="hotel"><div class="ic">🏨</div><div><b>Hotel Torifito Otaru Canal</b> <span style="color:#A9BFDC">· ホテル・トリフィート小樽運河</span><div class="sub">2 nights · steps from the canal · <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Hotel%20Torifito%20Otaru%20Canal" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Open in Maps ↗</a></div></div></div>
  <div class="tl"><div class="stop"><div class="time">10:30</div><div class="card"><h3>Nikka Whisky Yoichi Distillery <span class="badge hot">📕 小红书HOT</span></h3><div class="names">余市蒸溜所</div><div class="note">Stone kilns under snow, free museum. Tasting for you + wife only — drinking age in Japan is 20, so the 19yo sits out.</div><div class="links"><a class="map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Nikka%20Whisky%20Yoichi%20Distillery" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📍 Maps</a><a class="xhs" href="https://www.xiaohongshu.com/search_result?keyword=%E4%BD%99%E5%B8%82%E8%92%B8%E9%A6%8F%E6%89%80" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📕 小红书</a><a class="yt" href="https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=Nikka%20Yoichi%20distillery" target="_blank" rel="noopener">▶ YouTube</a></div></div></div><div class="stop"><div class="time">12:30</div><div class="card"><h3>Naruto Honten half-fried chicken <span class="badge eat">🍜 EAT</span></h3><div class="names">若鶏時代なると本店</div><div class="note">Showa-era icon since 1952 — the anti-generic Otaru lunch. Order the wakadori half chicken.</div><div class="links"><a class="map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Naruto%20Honten%20Otaru" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📍 Maps</a><a class="xhs" href="https://www.xiaohongshu.com/search_result?keyword=%E5%B0%8F%E6%A8%BD%20%E8%8B%A5%E9%B8%A1%E6%97%B6%E4%BB%A3" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📕 小红书</a><a class="yt" href="https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=Naruto%20Honten%20Otaru" target="_blank" rel="noopener">▶ YouTube</a></div></div></div><div class="stop"><div class="time">14:00</div><div class="card"><h3>Sakaimachi Street walk <span class="badge hot">📕 小红书HOT</span> <span class="badge eat">🍜 EAT</span></h3><div class="names">堺町通り</div><div class="note">Kitaichi Glass Sangokan (167 oil lamps lit at once), Music Box Museum + steam clock, LeTAO fondue.</div><div class="links"><a class="map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Sakaimachi%20Street%20Otaru" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📍 Maps</a><a class="xhs" href="https://www.xiaohongshu.com/search_result?keyword=%E5%B0%8F%E6%A8%BD%20%E5%A0%BA%E7%94%BA%E9%80%9A" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📕 小红书</a><a class="ig" href="https://www.instagram.com/explore/tags/otaru/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📸 IG</a></div></div></div><div class="stop night"><div class="time">15:45</div><div class="card"><h3>Asakusa Bridge — canal blue hour <span class="badge hot">📕 小红书HOT</span> <span class="badge nightb">🌙 NIGHT</span></h3><div class="names">浅草橋 · 小樽運河</div><div class="note">THE Otaru shot: gas lamps on at dusk, snow on the warehouses. Stand on Asakusa Bridge 15:50–16:20. Do not be late.</div><div class="links"><a class="map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Asakusa%20Bridge%20Otaru%20Canal" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📍 Maps</a><a class="xhs" href="https://www.xiaohongshu.com/search_result?keyword=%E5%B0%8F%E6%A8%BD%E8%BF%90%E6%B2%B3%20%E5%A4%9C%E6%99%AF" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📕 小红书</a><a class="ig" href="https://www.instagram.com/explore/tags/otarucanal/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📸 IG</a><a class="yt" href="https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=Otaru%20canal%20winter%20night" target="_blank" rel="noopener">▶ YouTube</a></div></div></div><div class="stop"><div class="time">18:00</div><div class="card"><h3>Sushi dinner <span class="badge eat">🍜 EAT</span></h3><div class="names">小樽 寿司</div><div class="note">Sushi town. Masazushi for the name, Ise Sushi for the counter. Book ahead either way.</div><div class="links"><a class="map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Masazushi%20Otaru" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📍 Maps</a><a class="xhs" href="https://www.xiaohongshu.com/search_result?keyword=%E5%B0%8F%E6%A8%BD%20%E5%AF%BF%E5%8F%B8" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📕 小红书</a></div></div></div></div></section><section class="daysec" id="day6">
  <div class="dayhead"><div class="eyebrow">Dec 15 · Tue</div><h2>Otaru Full Day + Night View</h2><div class="cn">小樽一日 · 天狗山夜景</div><div class="chips"><span class="chip">🐟 Market breakfast</span><span class="chip warn">🔥 Glass workshop — book slot</span><span class="chip">🌃 Tenguyama at dusk</span></div></div>
  <div class="hotel"><div class="ic">🏨</div><div><b>Hotel Torifito Otaru Canal</b> <span style="color:#A9BFDC">· ホテル・トリフィート小樽運河</span><div class="sub">Night 2 · <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Hotel%20Torifito%20Otaru%20Canal" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Open in Maps ↗</a></div></div></div>
  <div class="tl"><div class="stop"><div class="time">08:00</div><div class="card"><h3>Sankaku Market kaisendon <span class="badge eat">🍜 EAT</span> <span class="badge hot">📕 小红书HOT</span></h3><div class="names">三角市場 · 滝波食堂</div><div class="note">Build-your-own seafood bowl at Takinami Shokudo before the queues. Uni + ikura + crab.</div><div class="links"><a class="map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Sankaku%20Market%20Otaru" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📍 Maps</a><a class="xhs" href="https://www.xiaohongshu.com/search_result?keyword=%E5%B0%8F%E6%A8%BD%E4%B8%89%E8%A7%92%E5%B8%82%E5%9C%BA" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📕 小红书</a><a class="yt" href="https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=Sankaku%20market%20kaisendon" target="_blank" rel="noopener">▶ YouTube</a></div></div></div><div class="stop"><div class="time">09:30</div><div class="card"><h3>Nichigin-dori bank district </h3><div class="names">日銀通り · 旧日本銀行小樽支店</div><div class="note">'Wall Street of the North' — the former Bank of Japan is now a free museum. Handsome stone streets.</div><div class="links"><a class="map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Bank%20of%20Japan%20Otaru%20Museum" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📍 Maps</a></div></div></div><div class="stop"><div class="time">10:30</div><div class="card"><h3>Glass-blowing workshop <span class="badge hot">📕 小红书HOT</span></h3><div class="names">吹きガラス体験</div><div class="note">K's Blowing / Taisho Glass — ~20 min per person, and you fly home with the piece. Teens love it. Reserve a slot.</div><div class="links"><a class="map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=glass%20blowing%20workshop%20Otaru" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📍 Maps</a><a class="xhs" href="https://www.xiaohongshu.com/search_result?keyword=%E5%B0%8F%E6%A8%BD%20%E7%8E%BB%E7%92%83%E4%BD%93%E9%AA%8C" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📕 小红书</a><a class="yt" href="https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=Otaru%20glass%20blowing" target="_blank" rel="noopener">▶ YouTube</a></div></div></div><div class="stop"><div class="time">12:30</div><div class="card"><h3>Denuki-koji alley lunch <span class="badge eat">🍜 EAT</span></h3><div class="names">出抜小路</div><div class="note">Retro food-stall alley by the canal; grab the fire-lookout tower photo above it.</div><div class="links"><a class="map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Denuki%20Koji%20Otaru" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📍 Maps</a></div></div></div><div class="stop night"><div class="time">15:15</div><div class="card"><h3>Tenguyama Ropeway night view <span class="badge hot">📕 小红书HOT</span> <span class="badge nightb">🌙 NIGHT</span></h3><div class="names">天狗山ロープウェイ</div><div class="note">Up before sunset, stay through dusk — one of Hokkaido's three ranked night views, done while you're IN Otaru. Down ~17:15.</div><div class="links"><a class="map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Tenguyama%20Ropeway%20Otaru" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📍 Maps</a><a class="xhs" href="https://www.xiaohongshu.com/search_result?keyword=%E5%A4%A9%E7%8B%97%E5%B1%B1%20%E5%A4%9C%E6%99%AF" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📕 小红书</a><a class="yt" href="https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=Tenguyama%20night%20view" target="_blank" rel="noopener">▶ YouTube</a></div></div></div><div class="stop night"><div class="time">18:30</div><div class="card"><h3>Otaru Soko No.1 brewpub <span class="badge eat">🍜 EAT</span> <span class="badge nightb">🌙 NIGHT</span></h3><div class="names">小樽倉庫No.1</div><div class="note">Fresh beer inside an actual canal warehouse — proper end to the Otaru chapter.</div><div class="links"><a class="map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Otaru%20Soko%20No%201" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📍 Maps</a></div></div></div></div></section><section class="daysec" id="day7">
  <div class="dayhead"><div class="eyebrow">Dec 16 · Wed</div><h2>Asahiyama Zoo Day</h2><div class="cn">旭川 · 旭山動物園</div><div class="chips"><span class="chip">🚗 2h30 expressway — leave 08:00</span><span class="chip">🐧 Penguin walk 11:00</span></div></div>
  <div class="hotel"><div class="ic">🏨</div><div><b>Hotel Amanek Asahikawa</b> <span style="color:#A9BFDC">· ホテルアマネク旭川</span><div class="sub">2 rooms · <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Hotel%20Amanek%20Asahikawa" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Open in Maps ↗</a></div></div></div>
  <div class="tl"><div class="stop"><div class="time">10:45</div><div class="card"><h3>Asahiyama Zoo → 11:00 Penguin Walk <span class="badge hot">📕 小红书HOT</span></h3><div class="names">旭山動物園 ペンギンの散歩</div><div class="note">Go straight to the staging area — the 11:00 walk is calmer than 14:30. Then seals' Marine Way tube + polar bear dome. Lunch in the zoo.</div><div class="links"><a class="map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Asahiyama%20Zoo" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📍 Maps</a><a class="xhs" href="https://www.xiaohongshu.com/search_result?keyword=%E6%97%AD%E5%B1%B1%E5%8A%A8%E7%89%A9%E5%9B%AD%20%E4%BC%81%E9%B9%85%E6%95%A3%E6%AD%A5" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📕 小红书</a><a class="ig" href="https://www.instagram.com/explore/tags/asahiyamazoo/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📸 IG</a><a class="yt" href="https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=Asahiyama%20zoo%20penguin%20walk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">▶ YouTube</a></div></div></div><div class="stop"><div class="time">14:15</div><div class="card"><h3>Otokoyama Sake Brewery <span class="badge eat">🍜 EAT</span></h3><div class="names">男山酒造り資料舘</div><div class="note">300-year brewery museum, 45 min, free tastings (driver abstains — buy a bottle instead).</div><div class="links"><a class="map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Otokoyama%20Sake%20Brewing%20Museum" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📍 Maps</a><a class="xhs" href="https://www.xiaohongshu.com/search_result?keyword=%E7%94%B7%E5%B1%B1%E9%85%92%E9%80%A0" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📕 小红书</a></div></div></div><div class="stop"><div class="time">17:30</div><div class="card"><h3>Asahikawa shoyu ramen <span class="badge eat">🍜 EAT</span></h3><div class="names">旭川ラーメン · 青葉/蜂屋</div><div class="note">Aoba is the 1947 original but closes early — be there by 18:00. Hachiya's lard-sealed broth is the alternative. Heiwa-dori illumination on the walk back.</div><div class="links"><a class="map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Aoba%20Ramen%20Asahikawa" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📍 Maps</a><a class="xhs" href="https://www.xiaohongshu.com/search_result?keyword=%E6%97%AD%E5%B7%9D%E6%8B%89%E9%9D%A2" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📕 小红书</a><a class="yt" href="https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=Asahikawa%20ramen%20Aoba" target="_blank" rel="noopener">▶ YouTube</a></div></div></div></div></section><section class="daysec" id="day8">
  <div class="dayhead"><div class="eyebrow">Dec 17 · Thu</div><h2>Biei — The Trip's Peak Day</h2><div class="cn">美瑛 · 青い池 · 白金温泉</div><div class="chips"><span class="chip">🌲 Patchwork Road</span><span class="chip night">🌙 Blue Pond twice: day + illumination</span><span class="chip">♨️ Ryokan with meals</span></div></div>
  <div class="hotel"><div class="ic">🏨</div><div><b>Aonobi Yuyu (Shirogane Onsen)</b> <span style="color:#A9BFDC">· 青の美 湯游 · 白金温泉</span><div class="sub">Dinner + breakfast ×4 · 5 min from Blue Pond · <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Shirogane%20Onsen%20Biei" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Open in Maps ↗</a></div></div></div>
  <div class="tl"><div class="stop"><div class="time">08:30</div><div class="card"><h3>Patchwork Road trees <span class="badge hot">📕 小红书HOT</span></h3><div class="names">パッチワークの路</div><div class="note">Ken & Mary Tree, Seven Stars Tree, Parent & Child Trees — lone trees on white hills. Note: some famous poplars have been felled in recent years; don't route-build around Mild Seven.</div><div class="links"><a class="map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Patchwork%20Road%20Biei" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📍 Maps</a><a class="xhs" href="https://www.xiaohongshu.com/search_result?keyword=%E7%BE%8E%E7%91%9B%20%E6%8B%BC%E5%B8%83%E4%B9%8B%E8%B7%AF" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📕 小红书</a><a class="ig" href="https://www.instagram.com/explore/tags/biei/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📸 IG</a><a class="yt" href="https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=Biei%20winter%20drive" target="_blank" rel="noopener">▶ YouTube</a></div></div></div><div class="stop"><div class="time">11:30</div><div class="card"><h3>Junpei tonkatsu <span class="badge eat">🍜 EAT</span></h3><div class="names">じゅんぺい</div><div class="note">Biei's queue-before-open ebi-katsu institution. Arrive at opening or accept the wait.</div><div class="links"><a class="map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Junpei%20Biei" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📍 Maps</a><a class="xhs" href="https://www.xiaohongshu.com/search_result?keyword=%E7%BE%8E%E7%91%9B%20Junpei" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📕 小红书</a></div></div></div><div class="stop"><div class="time">13:00</div><div class="card"><h3>Christmas Tree no Ki <span class="badge hot">📕 小红书HOT</span></h3><div class="names">クリスマスツリーの木</div><div class="note">A lone spruce in an empty white field — on December 17. Yes. Shoot from the road; never enter the farm field.</div><div class="links"><a class="map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Christmas%20Tree%20no%20Ki%20Biei" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📍 Maps</a><a class="xhs" href="https://www.xiaohongshu.com/search_result?keyword=%E7%BE%8E%E7%91%9B%20%E5%9C%A3%E8%AF%9E%E6%A0%91%E4%B9%8B%E6%9C%A8" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📕 小红书</a><a class="ig" href="https://www.instagram.com/explore/tags/bieihokkaido/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📸 IG</a></div></div></div><div class="stop"><div class="time">14:00</div><div class="card"><h3>Blue Pond (daylight pass) <span class="badge hot">📕 小红书HOT</span></h3><div class="names">青い池 · Shirogane Blue Pond</div><div class="note">Milky-blue water + dead larches + snow. First pass in daylight; you're coming back tonight.</div><div class="links"><a class="map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Shirogane%20Blue%20Pond" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📍 Maps</a><a class="xhs" href="https://www.xiaohongshu.com/search_result?keyword=%E7%99%BD%E9%87%91%20%E9%9D%92%E3%81%84%E6%B1%A0" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📕 小红书</a><a class="ig" href="https://www.instagram.com/explore/tags/bluepond/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📸 IG</a><a class="yt" href="https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=Blue%20Pond%20Biei%20winter" target="_blank" rel="noopener">▶ YouTube</a></div></div></div><div class="stop"><div class="time">14:45</div><div class="card"><h3>Shirahige Waterfall <span class="badge hot">📕 小红书HOT</span></h3><div class="names">白ひげの滝</div><div class="note">'White beard' falls seeping from the cliff face into a cobalt river — shot from the bridge.</div><div class="links"><a class="map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Shirahige%20Waterfall%20Biei" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📍 Maps</a><a class="xhs" href="https://www.xiaohongshu.com/search_result?keyword=%E7%99%BD%E8%83%A1%E5%AD%90%E7%80%91%E5%B8%83" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📕 小红书</a></div></div></div><div class="stop night"><div class="time">19:30</div><div class="card"><h3>NIGHT ROUND: Blue Pond + Falls illumination <span class="badge hot">📕 小红书HOT</span> <span class="badge nightb">🌙 NIGHT</span></h3><div class="names">青い池ライトアップ</div><div class="note">Winter light-up typically ~17:00–21:00 (verify dates). You're staying 5 min away — almost nobody does this at night without a tour bus. The single best photo op of the trip.</div><div class="links"><a class="map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Shirogane%20Blue%20Pond%20illumination" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📍 Maps</a><a class="xhs" href="https://www.xiaohongshu.com/search_result?keyword=%E9%9D%92%E6%B1%A0%20%E5%A4%9C%E9%97%B4%E7%82%B9%E7%81%AF" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📕 小红书</a><a class="yt" href="https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=Blue%20Pond%20illumination%20winter" target="_blank" rel="noopener">▶ YouTube</a></div></div></div></div></section><section class="daysec" id="day9">
  <div class="dayhead"><div class="eyebrow">Dec 18 · Fri</div><h2>Furano — Cheese, Wine, Fairy Lights</h2><div class="cn">富良野</div><div class="chips"><span class="chip">♨️ Slow onsen morning</span><span class="chip">🍷 Winery = your hotel's vineyard</span></div></div>
  <div class="hotel"><div class="ic">🏨</div><div><b>Winery Hotel HITOHANA</b> <span style="color:#A9BFDC">· ワイナリーホテル一花</span><div class="sub">Kitanomine slope — you kept it for the winery, use it fully · <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Winery%20Hotel%20HITOHANA%20Furano" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Open in Maps ↗</a></div></div></div>
  <div class="tl"><div class="stop"><div class="time">11:00</div><div class="card"><h3>Furano Cheese Factory <span class="badge eat">🍜 EAT</span></h3><div class="names">富良野チーズ工房</div><div class="note">Butter/ice-cream mini workshops if the boys are game; squid-ink 'wine cheddar' for the road.</div><div class="links"><a class="map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Furano%20Cheese%20Factory" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📍 Maps</a><a class="xhs" href="https://www.xiaohongshu.com/search_result?keyword=%E5%AF%8C%E8%89%AF%E9%87%8E%E8%8A%9D%E5%A3%AB%E5%B7%A5%E6%88%BF" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📕 小红书</a></div></div></div><div class="stop"><div class="time">12:30</div><div class="card"><h3>Omu-curry at Masaya <span class="badge eat">🍜 EAT</span></h3><div class="names">まさ屋 富良野オムカレー</div><div class="note">Furano's official local dish — omelette curry done on a teppan. The certified version comes with local milk.</div><div class="links"><a class="map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Masaya%20Furano%20omu%20curry" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📍 Maps</a><a class="xhs" href="https://www.xiaohongshu.com/search_result?keyword=%E5%AF%8C%E8%89%AF%E9%87%8E%20%E8%9B%8B%E5%8C%85%E5%92%96%E5%96%B1" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📕 小红书</a></div></div></div><div class="stop"><div class="time">14:30</div><div class="card"><h3>Furano Winery tasting </h3><div class="names">ふらのワイン工場</div><div class="note">It's your hotel's own vineyard — this is why HITOHANA stayed on the booking. Driver spits, buys a bottle for Sapporo nights.</div><div class="links"><a class="map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Furano%20Winery" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📍 Maps</a><a class="yt" href="https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=Furano%20winery" target="_blank" rel="noopener">▶ YouTube</a></div></div></div><div class="stop night"><div class="time">15:45</div><div class="card"><h3>Ningle Terrace at dusk <span class="badge hot">📕 小红书HOT</span> <span class="badge nightb">🌙 NIGHT</span></h3><div class="names">ニングルテラス</div><div class="note">15 lamplit log-hut craft shops in a snowy forest — XHS top-10 Hokkaido. Hand-grind your own coffee at Mori no Tokei (森の時計).</div><div class="links"><a class="map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Ningle%20Terrace%20Furano" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📍 Maps</a><a class="xhs" href="https://www.xiaohongshu.com/search_result?keyword=%E6%A3%AE%E6%9E%97%E7%B2%BE%E7%81%B5%E9%9C%B2%E5%8F%B0" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📕 小红书</a><a class="ig" href="https://www.instagram.com/explore/tags/ningleterrace/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📸 IG</a><a class="yt" href="https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=Ningle%20Terrace%20night" target="_blank" rel="noopener">▶ YouTube</a></div></div></div><div class="stop"><div class="time">18:30</div><div class="card"><h3>Kumagera izakaya <span class="badge eat">🍜 EAT</span></h3><div class="names">くまげら</div><div class="note">Local institution — wagyu hotpot and sansai dishes. Book if you can.</div><div class="links"><a class="map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Kumagera%20Furano" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📍 Maps</a><a class="xhs" href="https://www.xiaohongshu.com/search_result?keyword=%E5%AF%8C%E8%89%AF%E9%87%8E%20%E7%86%8A%E5%95%84%E6%9C%A8%E9%B8%9F" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📕 小红书</a></div></div></div></div></section><section class="daysec" id="day10">
  <div class="dayhead"><div class="eyebrow">Dec 19 · Sat</div><h2>Ice Fishing → Snowmobile → Ice Village</h2><div class="cn">南富良野 → 星野TOMAMU愛絲冰城</div><div class="chips"><span class="chip">🎣 Eat your catch</span><span class="chip warn">🛷 Snowmobile booked by Dec 17</span><span class="chip night">🌙 Sanctioned night drive · back 20:45</span></div></div>
  <div class="hotel"><div class="ic">🏨</div><div><b>Fairfield by Marriott Minamifurano</b> <span style="color:#A9BFDC">· フェアフィールド南富良野</span><div class="sub">2 rooms confirmed ✓ · Tomamu 35 min away · <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Fairfield%20by%20Marriott%20Hokkaido%20Minamifurano" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Open in Maps ↗</a></div></div></div>
  <div class="tl"><div class="stop"><div class="time">09:30</div><div class="card"><h3>Smelt fishing on Lake Kanayama <span class="badge hot">📕 小红书HOT</span> <span class="badge eat">🍜 EAT</span></h3><div class="names">かなやま湖 ワカサギ釣り</div><div class="note">Tent on the ice, drop a line, and they tempura your wakasagi on the spot. Breakfast you caught yourself.</div><div class="links"><a class="map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Lake%20Kanayama%20smelt%20fishing" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📍 Maps</a><a class="xhs" href="https://www.xiaohongshu.com/search_result?keyword=%E9%87%91%E5%B1%B1%E6%B9%96%20%E5%86%B0%E9%92%93" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📕 小红书</a><a class="yt" href="https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=Lake%20Kanayama%20wakasagi%20fishing" target="_blank" rel="noopener">▶ YouTube</a></div></div></div><div class="stop"><div class="time">13:30</div><div class="card"><h3>Snowmobile 10 km course <span class="badge hot">📕 小红书HOT</span></h3><div class="names">スノーモービル</div><div class="note">The optbookmark plan you found — needed booking 2 days ahead, so by Dec 17. Layer up; it's colder at speed.</div><div class="links"><a class="map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=snowmobile%20Minamifurano" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📍 Maps</a><a class="yt" href="https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=Hokkaido%20snowmobile%20tour" target="_blank" rel="noopener">▶ YouTube</a></div></div></div><div class="stop night"><div class="time">17:15</div><div class="card"><h3>Tomamu Ice Village <span class="badge hot">📕 小红书HOT</span> <span class="badge nightb">🌙 NIGHT</span></h3><div class="names">星野リゾート トマム アイスヴィレッジ · 爱丝冰城</div><div class="note">Opens ~Dec 10 seasonally, 17:00–22:00, ¥600. Ice slide, rink, Ice Bar (drinks in ice glasses), the anniversary Ice Chapel. Dinner at Hotalu Street.</div><div class="links"><a class="map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Ice%20Village%20Tomamu" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📍 Maps</a><a class="xhs" href="https://www.xiaohongshu.com/search_result?keyword=%E7%88%B1%E4%B8%9D%E5%86%B0%E5%9F%8E%20Tomamu" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📕 小红书</a><a class="ig" href="https://www.instagram.com/explore/tags/tomamu/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📸 IG</a><a class="yt" href="https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=Tomamu%20ice%20village" target="_blank" rel="noopener">▶ YouTube</a></div></div></div><div class="stop night"><div class="time">20:00</div><div class="card"><h3>Night drive back <span class="badge nightb">🌙 NIGHT</span></h3><div class="names">夜間走行 · 慢</div><div class="note">Your ONE planned night drive. Major ploughed road (Rt 38→136), go slow, dip high beams for oncoming. In bed by 21:00.</div><div class="links"><a class="map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Fairfield%20by%20Marriott%20Hokkaido%20Minamifurano" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📍 Maps</a></div></div></div></div><div class="tipbox"><b>Deadline:</b> snowmobile must be booked 2 days ahead → by <b>Dec 17</b>. Smelt-fishing operator too.</div></section><section class="daysec" id="day11">
  <div class="dayhead"><div class="eyebrow">Dec 20 · Sun</div><h2>Sapporo — Car Off, Lights On</h2><div class="cn">札幌 · 白色燈樹節</div><div class="chips"><span class="chip">🚗 Return car ~11:45</span><span class="chip">👓 Zoff: order early, collect late</span><span class="chip">🎄 Market runs to Dec 25</span></div></div>
  <div class="hotel"><div class="ic">🏨</div><div><b>ibis Styles Sapporo</b> <span style="color:#A9BFDC">· イビススタイルズ札幌</span><div class="sub">3 nights · 2 rooms confirmed ✓ · everything tonight on foot · <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=ibis%20Styles%20Sapporo" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Open in Maps ↗</a></div></div></div>
  <div class="tl"><div class="stop"><div class="time">11:45</div><div class="card"><h3>Return car — Orix Sapporo </h3><div class="names">オリックスレンタカー札幌</div><div class="note">Fuel it first (rental agreements want a full tank + receipt). Bags dropped at ibis beforehand.</div><div class="links"><a class="map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Orix%20Rent%20a%20Car%20Sapporo" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📍 Maps</a></div></div></div><div class="stop"><div class="time">12:30</div><div class="card"><h3>Soup curry lunch <span class="badge eat">🍜 EAT</span> <span class="badge hot">📕 小红书HOT</span></h3><div class="names">スープカレー · Suage+/GARAKU</div><div class="note">Sapporo's own dish. Suage+ (skewered fried veg) or Garaku (richer broth). There will be a queue; it's worth it.</div><div class="links"><a class="map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Suage%2B%20Sapporo" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📍 Maps</a><a class="xhs" href="https://www.xiaohongshu.com/search_result?keyword=%E6%9C%AD%E5%B9%8C%E6%B1%A4%E5%92%96%E5%96%B1" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📕 小红书</a><a class="yt" href="https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=Sapporo%20soup%20curry" target="_blank" rel="noopener">▶ YouTube</a></div></div></div><div class="stop"><div class="time">13:45</div><div class="card"><h3>Zoff — eye test + ORDER first </h3><div class="names">Zoff 札幌</div><div class="note">Order at 13:45 (~30 min), lenses take ~1–2h. Shop while they're made; collect 16:30. Backup: Dec 21–22 if lenses need next-day.</div><div class="links"><a class="map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Zoff%20Sapporo%20Pole%20Town" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📍 Maps</a></div></div></div><div class="stop"><div class="time">14:30</div><div class="card"><h3>Tanukikoji + Don Quijote + Pole Town <span class="badge eat">🍜 EAT</span></h3><div class="names">狸小路 · ドン・キホーテ</div><div class="note">Covered arcade shopping while the lenses are cut. The boys disappear into Donki; set a meeting time.</div><div class="links"><a class="map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Tanukikoji%20Shopping%20Street" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📍 Maps</a><a class="xhs" href="https://www.xiaohongshu.com/search_result?keyword=%E7%8B%B8%E5%B0%8F%E8%B7%AF%20%E8%B4%AD%E7%89%A9" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📕 小红书</a></div></div></div><div class="stop night"><div class="time">16:45</div><div class="card"><h3>White Illumination + Munich Christmas Market <span class="badge hot">📕 小红书HOT</span> <span class="badge nightb">🌙 NIGHT</span> <span class="badge eat">🍜 EAT</span></h3><div class="names">さっぽろホワイトイルミネーション · 慕尼黑聖誕市集</div><div class="note">Both run to Dec 25 — you're in the final festive window. Mulled wine, hot grape juice for the 14yo, pretzels, keep the mug. Odori Park glowing under snow.</div><div class="links"><a class="map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Odori%20Park%20Sapporo" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📍 Maps</a><a class="xhs" href="https://www.xiaohongshu.com/search_result?keyword=%E6%9C%AD%E5%B9%8C%E7%99%BD%E8%89%B2%E7%81%AF%E6%A0%91%E8%8A%82" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📕 小红书</a><a class="ig" href="https://www.instagram.com/explore/tags/sapporowhiteillumination/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📸 IG</a><a class="yt" href="https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=Sapporo%20white%20illumination" target="_blank" rel="noopener">▶ YouTube</a></div></div></div></div></section><section class="daysec" id="day12">
  <div class="dayhead"><div class="eyebrow">Dec 21 · Mon</div><h2>Market, Miso, Lamb</h2><div class="cn">札幌 · 食と買い物</div><div class="chips"><span class="chip">🦀 Market breakfast</span><span class="chip">🍜 Miso ramen at the source</span><span class="chip warn">🐑 Daruma queue at 17:00 SHARP</span></div></div>
  <div class="hotel"><div class="ic">🏨</div><div><b>ibis Styles Sapporo</b> <span style="color:#A9BFDC">· イビススタイルズ札幌</span><div class="sub">Night 2 · <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=ibis%20Styles%20Sapporo" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Open in Maps ↗</a></div></div></div>
  <div class="tl"><div class="stop"><div class="time">08:00</div><div class="card"><h3>Nijo Market kaisendon <span class="badge eat">🍜 EAT</span> <span class="badge hot">📕 小红书HOT</span></h3><div class="names">二条市場</div><div class="note">Century-old market — crab legs and uni-ikura don for breakfast. Go early, stalls wind down by afternoon.</div><div class="links"><a class="map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Nijo%20Market%20Sapporo" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📍 Maps</a><a class="xhs" href="https://www.xiaohongshu.com/search_result?keyword=%E4%BA%8C%E6%9D%A1%E5%B8%82%E5%9C%BA%20%E6%B5%B7%E9%B2%9C%E9%A5%AD" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📕 小红书</a></div></div></div><div class="stop"><div class="time">10:00</div><div class="card"><h3>Station shopping: Stellar Place / Daimaru </h3><div class="names">札幌駅 · ステラプレイス</div><div class="note">Second shopping wave; collect Zoff if it went to next-day.</div><div class="links"><a class="map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Sapporo%20Stellar%20Place" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📍 Maps</a></div></div></div><div class="stop"><div class="time">13:00</div><div class="card"><h3>Sumire miso ramen <span class="badge eat">🍜 EAT</span></h3><div class="names">すみれ 中の島本店</div><div class="note">The miso ramen benchmark — lard-capped broth that stays scalding in −5° weather. This is the bowl Sapporo is famous FOR.</div><div class="links"><a class="map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Sumire%20Ramen%20Susukino" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📍 Maps</a><a class="xhs" href="https://www.xiaohongshu.com/search_result?keyword=%E6%9C%AD%E5%B9%8C%20sumire%20%E5%91%B3%E5%99%8C%E6%8B%89%E9%9D%A2" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📕 小红书</a><a class="yt" href="https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=Sumire%20miso%20ramen" target="_blank" rel="noopener">▶ YouTube</a></div></div></div><div class="stop night"><div class="time">15:30</div><div class="card"><h3>JR Tower T38 observatory <span class="badge hot">📕 小红书HOT</span> <span class="badge nightb">🌙 NIGHT</span></h3><div class="names">JRタワー展望室T38</div><div class="note">38F over the snow-grid at dusk — even the designer toilets have the view. Quieter than TV Tower.</div><div class="links"><a class="map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=JR%20Tower%20Observatory%20T38" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📍 Maps</a><a class="xhs" href="https://www.xiaohongshu.com/search_result?keyword=JR%E5%A1%94%20%E5%B1%95%E6%9C%9B%E5%8F%B0" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📕 小红书</a></div></div></div><div class="stop"><div class="time">17:00</div><div class="card"><h3>Jingisukan Daruma honten — queue NOW <span class="badge eat">🍜 EAT</span> <span class="badge hot">📕 小红书HOT</span></h3><div class="names">成吉思汗だるま本店</div><div class="note">The smoky lamb counter that defines Sapporo dinners. Doors fill instantly — be in line at 17:00 sharp or go 21:00+. Clothes will smell of lamb; wear the washables.</div><div class="links"><a class="map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Jingisukan%20Daruma%20Honten" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📍 Maps</a><a class="xhs" href="https://www.xiaohongshu.com/search_result?keyword=%E8%BE%BE%E6%91%A9%E6%88%90%E5%90%89%E6%80%9D%E6%B1%97%E7%83%A4%E8%82%89" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📕 小红书</a><a class="yt" href="https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=Daruma%20jingisukan%20Sapporo" target="_blank" rel="noopener">▶ YouTube</a></div></div></div></div></section><section class="daysec" id="day13">
  <div class="dayhead"><div class="eyebrow">Dec 22 · Tue</div><h2>Chocolate, Beer, Night-View Finale</h2><div class="cn">札幌 · 白い恋人 · 藻岩山</div><div class="chips"><span class="chip">🍪 Cookie workshop</span><span class="chip">🍺 Beer Museum</span><span class="chip">🌃 Moiwa = trip finale shot</span></div></div>
  <div class="hotel"><div class="ic">🏨</div><div><b>ibis Styles Sapporo</b> <span style="color:#A9BFDC">· イビススタイルズ札幌</span><div class="sub">Final night — pack tonight · <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=ibis%20Styles%20Sapporo" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Open in Maps ↗</a></div></div></div>
  <div class="tl"><div class="stop"><div class="time">09:00</div><div class="card"><h3>Shiroi Koibito Park <span class="badge hot">📕 小红书HOT</span></h3><div class="names">白い恋人パーク</div><div class="note">The chocolate factory behind Hokkaido's most famous omiyage — Tudor courtyard under snow, cookie-making workshop for the boys.</div><div class="links"><a class="map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Shiroi%20Koibito%20Park" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📍 Maps</a><a class="xhs" href="https://www.xiaohongshu.com/search_result?keyword=%E7%99%BD%E8%89%B2%E6%81%8B%E4%BA%BA%E5%85%AC%E5%9B%AD" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📕 小红书</a><a class="ig" href="https://www.instagram.com/explore/tags/shiroikoibitopark/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📸 IG</a><a class="yt" href="https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=Shiroi%20Koibito%20Park%20winter" target="_blank" rel="noopener">▶ YouTube</a></div></div></div><div class="stop"><div class="time">12:00</div><div class="card"><h3>Sapporo Beer Museum + Genghis Khan hall <span class="badge eat">🍜 EAT</span></h3><div class="names">サッポロビール博物館</div><div class="note">Japan's only beer museum, then all-you-can-grill lamb in the red-brick Beer Garden hall. 19yo still on oolong — age is 20.</div><div class="links"><a class="map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Sapporo%20Beer%20Museum" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📍 Maps</a><a class="xhs" href="https://www.xiaohongshu.com/search_result?keyword=%E6%9C%AD%E5%B9%8C%E5%95%A4%E9%85%92%E5%8D%9A%E7%89%A9%E9%A6%86" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📕 小红书</a></div></div></div><div class="stop"><div class="time">14:30</div><div class="card"><h3>Gift run: Kinotoya, Rokkatei, Royce <span class="badge eat">🍜 EAT</span></h3><div class="names">きのとや · 六花亭 · ロイズ</div><div class="note">Station basement: Kinotoya cheese tarts eaten warm, Marusei butter sandwiches + Royce nama chocolate boxed for Singapore.</div><div class="links"><a class="map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Kinotoya%20Sapporo%20station" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📍 Maps</a><a class="xhs" href="https://www.xiaohongshu.com/search_result?keyword=%E6%9C%AD%E5%B9%8C%20%E4%BC%B4%E6%89%8B%E7%A4%BC" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📕 小红书</a></div></div></div><div class="stop night"><div class="time">16:15</div><div class="card"><h3>Mt Moiwa Ropeway <span class="badge hot">📕 小红书HOT</span> <span class="badge nightb">🌙 NIGHT</span></h3><div class="names">藻岩山ロープウェイ</div><div class="note">One of Japan's 'new three great night views' — ride up at dusk, shoot the blue-to-black transition over the light grid. Trip finale.</div><div class="links"><a class="map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Mount%20Moiwa%20Ropeway" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📍 Maps</a><a class="xhs" href="https://www.xiaohongshu.com/search_result?keyword=%E8%97%BB%E5%B2%A9%E5%B1%B1%20%E5%A4%9C%E6%99%AF" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📕 小红书</a><a class="ig" href="https://www.instagram.com/explore/tags/mtmoiwa/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📸 IG</a><a class="yt" href="https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=Mt%20Moiwa%20night%20view" target="_blank" rel="noopener">▶ YouTube</a></div></div></div><div class="stop"><div class="time">19:00</div><div class="card"><h3>Farewell dinner: crab <span class="badge eat">🍜 EAT</span></h3><div class="names">かに本家</div><div class="note">Kanihonke for the full crab-kaiseki send-off, or a kaisen izakaya if you'd rather spend the yen on gifts.</div><div class="links"><a class="map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Kanihonke%20Sapporo" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📍 Maps</a><a class="xhs" href="https://www.xiaohongshu.com/search_result?keyword=%E6%9C%AD%E5%B9%8C%20%E8%9E%83%E8%9F%B9%E6%9C%AC%E5%AE%B6" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📕 小红书</a></div></div></div></div></section><section class="daysec" id="day14">
  <div class="dayhead"><div class="eyebrow">Dec 23–24</div><h2>Departure + Taipei Overnight</h2><div class="cn">新千歳 → 台北 → 新加坡</div><div class="chips"><span class="chip">🚆 Rapid Airport 08:15</span><span class="chip">✈️ CTS 12:10 → TPE 16:05</span><span class="chip">🛌 TPE overnight · BR225 07:25</span></div></div>
  <div class="hotel"><div class="ic">🏨</div><div><b>COZZI Blu Taoyuan (suggested)</b> <span style="color:#A9BFDC">· 和逸飯店桃園館</span><div class="sub">2 MRT stops from airport · Xpark & outlets in the same complex · <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=COZZI%20Blu%20Hotel%20Taoyuan" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Open in Maps ↗</a></div></div></div>
  <div class="tl"><div class="stop"><div class="time">07:45</div><div class="card"><h3>Checkout → JR Sapporo Station </h3><div class="names">札幌駅 快速エアポート</div><div class="note">Rapid Airport every ~12 min, 37 min to CTS. December snow delays are real — don't trim this buffer.</div><div class="links"><a class="map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=JR%20Sapporo%20Station" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📍 Maps</a></div></div></div><div class="stop"><div class="time">09:00</div><div class="card"><h3>CTS check-in — ask for THROUGH-CHECK </h3><div class="names">新千歳空港 EVA</div><div class="note">「荷物はシンガポールまでスルーでお願いします」— bags tagged SIN, both boarding passes issued. Verify the tag stub reads SIN. Overnight kit stays in carry-ons.</div><div class="links"><a class="map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=New%20Chitose%20Airport%20international%20terminal" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📍 Maps</a></div></div></div><div class="stop"><div class="time">17:00</div><div class="card"><h3>TPE: enter Taiwan, MRT to A18 </h3><div class="names">桃園機場捷運 → 高鐵桃園站</div><div class="note">Singapore passports enter visa-free (online arrival card done beforehand). No bags to collect. 2 stops to A18.</div><div class="links"><a class="map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Taoyuan%20HSR%20station" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📍 Maps</a></div></div></div><div class="stop"><div class="time">18:00</div><div class="card"><h3>Xpark aquarium + Gloria Outlets + dinner <span class="badge hot">📕 小红书HOT</span> <span class="badge eat">🍜 EAT</span></h3><div class="names">Xpark 水族館 · 華泰名品城</div><div class="note">Japanese-designed aquarium with evening sessions, sneaker outlets for the boys, dinner in the complex — hotel is upstairs. Smarter than a Taipei dash on day 15.</div><div class="links"><a class="map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Xpark%20Taoyuan" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📍 Maps</a><a class="xhs" href="https://www.xiaohongshu.com/search_result?keyword=Xpark%20%E6%A1%83%E5%9B%AD%E6%B0%B4%E6%97%8F%E9%A6%86" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📕 小红书</a><a class="yt" href="https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=Xpark%20Taoyuan%20aquarium" target="_blank" rel="noopener">▶ YouTube</a></div></div></div><div class="stop"><div class="time">05:00</div><div class="card"><h3>Next morning: 10 min to T2, fly 07:25 </h3><div class="names">第二航廈 → 新加坡</div><div class="note">Counters ~05:15 with boarding passes in hand. Home by 12:05. おつかれさま — trip complete.</div><div class="links"><a class="map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Taoyuan%20Airport%20Terminal%202" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📍 Maps</a></div></div></div></div><div class="checklist"><h3>Book-before-you-fly checklist</h3><ul><li>Hirafu dinners ×2 (Dec 12–13) — book NOW</li><li>Snowmobile 10 km (by Dec 17) + smelt fishing operator</li><li>Otaru glass-blowing slot + sushi dinner</li><li>Plaza Premium T2 relaxation suites for the Dec 8 overnight (outbound transit)</li><li>Verify: Blue Pond illumination dates · Ice Village 2026–27 opening · Tenguyama winter hours</li><li>Email/call EVA: confirm through-check CTS→SIN on the single PNR</li><li>Taiwan online arrival cards ×4</li></ul></div></section>
